item.title: Writing makefiles for micro kernels
item.description: This makefile contains the base for building tracer. $ make clean $ make upload Project overview Tracer’s component are the following : kernel : the standard operationnal base, in charge of managing shared ressources. These resources can be hardware (processor, coprocessors, peripheral, memory, etc…) or software (files, shared mem, interfaces, etc…). modules : the variable operationnal base, executing at kernel privilege level, and taking advantage of the kernel’s capabilities.
